                        <collation>Primarily quinternions throughout.
                           1VI+1(14)10V(114)1II(118)2V(138)1IV(146)4V(186)1III-1(191).
                              <catchwords>Catchwords throughout</catchwords>.</collation>
                        <condition>In good condition, with minor historical and modern repairs. A
                           stub remains between folios <locus from="191a" to="192b">191 and
                              192</locus>, apparently what remains of the final conjugate fold.
                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="1 2" ruledLines="25" n="mistara"> Written in 1–2 columns
